# vim-ruby-heredoc-syntax

Enable highlight markdown code block with appropriate syntax.

## Screenshot

![screenshot.png](screenshot.png)

## Option

```vim
" Add syntax rule
let g:ruby_heredoc_syntax_filetypes = {
        \ "xml" : {
        \   "start" : "XML",
        \},
  \}

" 'start' is heredoc start literal.
```

